<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    #set($version="201711071308")
    #set($src="http://f.51fanbei.com/h5/app/activity/11")
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>新人专享</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dist/activity/11/newUser.css?version=$version">
</head>
<body>
<div id="newUser" class="newUser">
    <div class="loadingMask"><i class="loading"></i></div>
    <div class="banner first"></div>
    <div class="activityDetail" @click="activityDetailClick">活动详情</div>
    <div class="alertRule">
        <p class="ruleTitle"><img src="$src/newUser05.png"></p>
        <p class="ruleCont">
            <span>1.新用户下载登录APP实名认证并获得可用额度后，即可在51返呗购买新人专享商品</span>
            <span>2.新人专场商品仅用户首个分期订单，且每人限购一件，如重复购买视为无效订单</span>
            <span>3.新人专场中的商品不支持退货</span>
        </p>
        <p class="closeRule" @click="closeClick">X</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mask" v-show="ruleShow" @click="closeClick"></div>
    <div class="shareBtn clearFix">
        <p class="shareNow" @click="shareNowClick"><img src="$src/newUser02.png"></p>
        <p class="inviteNow" @click="inviteNowClick"><img src="$src/newUser03.png"></p>
    </div>
    <p class="title"><img src="$src/newUser04.png"></p>
    <div class="goodList">
        <div class="good clearFix" @click="buyNowClick(item)" v-for="item in content">
            <p class="goodImg"><img class="lazy" :data-original="item.goodsIcon"></p>
            <div class="right clearFix">
                <p class="goodName" style="-webkit-box-orient: vertical;">{{item.goodsName}}</p>
                <p class="goodDes"><span>减</span>下单立减{{item.decreasePrice}}元，新会员专享</p>
                <p class="goodPrice">￥<span>{{item.realAmount}}</span></p>
                <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='0'">月供：¥{{item.nperMap.amount}}起</p>
                <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='1' || item.nperMap.isFree==='2'">月供：¥{{item.nperMap.freeAmount}}起</p>
                <p class="buyNow">立即抢购</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://img.51fanbei.com/h5/static/base64.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/dist/activity/11/newUser.js?version=$version"></script>
</body>
</html>
